---
title: Teriyaki Pak Choi Noodles  with chilli flake and sesame seed garnish
description: Sunny-side up or over easy? A perfectly cooked fried egg sprinkled with toasted sesame seeds and scallions is the crowning jewel of this deliciously savoury teriyaki veggie dish.
